In the update phrase, we will update a posteriori state using estimation below:
$$x_{k|k}=x_{k|k-1}  +K_ky_k$$
And the covariance matrix can be updated as:
$$P_{k|k}=(I-K_kH_k) P_{k|k-1}$$
